query:
SELECT gat.token, gat.is_active, gp.name 
FROM gp_access_tokens gat 
JOIN game_presenters gp ON gat.gp_id = gp.id 
WHERE gp.name LIKE '%Agnes%' OR gp.name LIKE '%Suvorov%';
